    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei eterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius </persName>divina favente clementia<rs key="#Emperor/king">
                            imperator</rs> augustus. Noverit omnium fidelium sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        nostrorumque presentium [scilicet] et futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke #fidelisOf" ref="#people/188"
                            >Grimaldum</persName> gloriosum <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionem</rs>
                        dilectumque <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelem </rs>nostrum humiliter nostram
                        exorasse <rs key="#Intercessory">clementiam</rs>, quatenus cuidam <rs
                            key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/92">sancte
                            Aquileiensis <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        </orgName>nomine <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petro</name></persName> presenti auctoritate concedere dignaremur
                        licentiam suum <rs key="#Castle">castellum proprium</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Castle #Defensive_elements #Cisterns/pits #Albergaria/gifori #Profits_of_justice #Immunity"
                            ref="#estates/500"><placeName
                                key="#Castle #Defensive_elements #Cisterns/pits #Albergaria/gifori #Profits_of_justice #Immunity"
                                ref="#places/900">Saborniano</placeName></geogName> dictum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">in sua videlicet proprietate</rs> constructum
                        confirmari et muniri <rs key="#Defensive_elements #Cisterns/pits">merulis et
                            propugnaculis, bertistis atque fossatis</rs>. Cuius precibus inclinati,
                        prenominato Petro presbitero hoc nostre concessionis precepto licentiam et
                        largitatem dedimus castellum suum Saborniano confirmari et muniri merulis et
                        propugnaculis, bertistis atque fossatis, precipientes et omnino [iubentes],
                        ut nullus dux, marchio, comes, vicecomes, sculdassio, gastaldio, decanus aut
                        aliqua magna parvaque persona in ipsum castellum <rs key="#Immunity"
                            >ingrediens</rs> aliquam inferat controvesiam vel molestationem. nemo
                        inhibi publicis ministerialibus teneat <rs key="#Profits_of_justice"
                            >placitum</rs> aut <rs key="#Albergaria/gifori">mansionaticum</rs>
                        faciat potestative, sed liceat eidem presbitero prenominatum castellum suum
                        iure quieto possidere usque in perpetuum, absque omni publica inquietudine
                        vel contradictione. et hoc ante omnia decernimus atque iubemus, ut <rs
                            key="#Village/castle_territory">homines ipsius presbiteri qui in suis
                            proprietatibus resident </rs>ante nullum publicum ministerialem <rs
                            key="#Profits_of_justice">placitum</rs> custodiant nisi in presentia <rs
                            key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs> qui pro tempore fuerit, tribus
                        vicibus in anno. Si quis vero hoc nostre concessionis preceptum infringere
                        tentaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras
                            quinquaginta</rs>, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere nostre
                        </rs>et medietatem predicto <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> suisque
                        heredibus aut cui ipse dederit vel habere concesserit. Quod ut verius
                        credatur et diligentius observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro
                        subter iussimus insigniri. Signum domni [(M)] Berengarii serenissimi
                        imperatoris augusti. <persName key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1501"
                            >Iohannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi
                            </persName><rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> recognovi [et subscripsi].
                        Dat. octavo kal. aprilis, anno dominice incamationis .DCCCCXXI., domni vero
                        Berengarii serenissimi regis .XXVIII. (D), imperii autem [sui] .VII.,
                        indictione .X. Actum <placeName ref="#places/59">Verone.</placeName> in Dei
                        nomine feliciter, amen. </ab>
